And scale around it: 

    private void zoom(ScrollEvent scrollEvent) {
        // adds or subtracts to the image&#39;s scale based on
        // whether user is scrolling backwards or forwards
        final double dScale = scrollEvent.getDeltaY() &gt; 0 ? 0.1 : -0.1;
